    "read": [
      "Adding dKV contribution math without any global dKV writes costs only about 0.09 ms over the no-dKV diagnostic.",
      "Adding raw racy dKV stores raises the full-head TileLang core to 9.26 ms, already slower than the current 8.01 ms Triton sparse-atomic wall.",
      "Therefore the main wall is the raw selected-row write volume itself; atomics make the straight reference much worse, but simply replacing atomics with normal stores is not a speed path."
